    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall in Test conditions (achieved level 1 vs. required level 2) is accepted on the basis that ASTM F1717 prescribes a single standardized test configuration and that supplemental computational sensitivity analyses confirm robustness across the plausible parameter range. Overall credibility is sufficient to support regulatory submission for the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw design.",
